To show data from Firebase in your react-native app, you'll need to use a library like Firebase SDK or Firebase REST API to connect to your Firebase database and retrieve the data.

Assuming you're using Firebase SDK, you can follow these steps:

1. Install the Firebase SDK and import it into your app:

